{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"WebSocket.onopen","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/open_event","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>**<code>WebSocket.onopen</code>**属性定义一个事件处理程序，当<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket\"><code>WebSocket</code></a> 的连接状态<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/readyState\" title=\"readyState\"><code>readyState</code></a> 变为<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/readyState\" title=\"1\"><code>1</code></a>时调用;这意味着当前连接已经准备好发送和接受数据。这个事件处理程序通过 <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此文档尚未被撰写，期待你的贡献!\"><code>事件</code></a>（建立连接时）触发。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: plain notranslate\">aWebSocket.onopen = function(event) {\n  console.log(\"WebSocket is open now.\");\n};\n</pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"返回值","title":"返回值","isH3":false,"content":"<p>An <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\"><code>EventListener</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/indices.html#event-open","title":"HTML Standard"},{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/web-sockets.html#handler-websocket-onopen","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.WebSocket.open_event"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.WebSocket.open_event","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/open_event/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"返回值","id":"返回值"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"}],"summary":"**WebSocket.onopen**属性定义一个事件处理程序，当WebSocket 的连接状态readyState 变为1时调用;这意味着当前连接已经准备好发送和接受数据。这个事件处理程序通过 事件（建立连接时）触发。","popularity":0.0007,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z"